    {
      "id": "section-47",
      "number": 47,
      "numberStr": "47",
      "key": "MISH_47",
      "title": "Insurance Requirements Contractual Risk Transfer",
      "slug": "insurance-requirements-contractual-risk-transfer",
      "previewHtml": "<h1>1.0 PURPOSE</h1><p><strong>1.1 </strong>Effective contractual risk transfer protects MH Construction from liability resulting from subcontractor operations and requires subcontractors to take financial responsibility for their own exposures.</p><p><strong>1.2 </strong>All MHC subcontracts must include the insurance requirements defined in this section. Review with your insurance agent (Hub International Northwest) and legal counsel before finalizing any subcontract.</p>"
    },
    {
